---
import checkmarkIcon from "../../assets/icons/checkmark.svg?raw";
---

<section>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:gap-16 gap-8 px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 md:py-24 max-w-6xl mx-auto"
  >
    <div class="max-w-sm">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-white sm:text-4xl md:text-6xl">Key benefits</h2>
    </div>

    <ul class="space-y-8 text-sm md:text-lg">
      <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 text-[green-400] shrink-0" set:html={checkmarkIcon} />
        <span>Extends battle-tested standards like DNSSEC, X.509 and CMS.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400 shrink-0" set:html={checkmarkIcon} />
        <span>Open protocol with open source reference implementations.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400 shrink-0" set:html={checkmarkIcon} />
        <span>As decentralised as DNS itself.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400 shrink-0" set:html={checkmarkIcon} />
        <span>Signatures can be produced and verified offline.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
